preference.preference_description: Finding out which haven't been checked recently is done by using the ApprQueryAudit's lastWorthinessUpdateDate and validationWorthiness. When such an object is created, its lastWorthinessUpdateDate is set to its creation-date and its validationWorthiness is given an initial value.
